capture_peak_action_activity::clip_card_: Sochii qaamichaa tilmaamiitii fiixee hojii gocha isaanii qabadhu.
capture_peak_action_activity::text_card_: Amma erga kutaa fiixee hojii xumurtee, gochaawwan kun akka ati shaakaltuuf si gargaaru. Gochaawwan irra deebii qaban kan akka ispoortii yookaan ijoollee taphatanii barbaadi. Suuraa sochii bilbilaan kaasuun keessumaa rakkisaadha.
capture_peak_action_activity::title: Gocha Fiixee Hojii Qabadhu
